****************************
This is the README file.
****************************

* The FSMLanguage compiler is located in /fpga_scripts/generate_fsm/src/
    * Requires installation of GHCi
    * http://www.haskell.org/ghc/

* The FSM Visualization tool is located in /fpga_scripts/fsm_visualizer/src/
    * Requires installation of DOT/DOTTY (GraphViz)
    * http://www.graphviz.org/
